Keep Backup Daily is a wordpress plugin which helps you to get relax about taking regular backups. It is much better that if you are running a news website and don't want to overload your database. Keep backup daily and another plugin might be freeing up your database on weekly basis. There can be many uses of this plugin, you could have a look what activity is performing on your database now a days.
